l, but output quality drops for anything over 500 words. Claude gives you more voice control, better structure, and consistently stronger output for customer-facing content."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does Notion AI work outside of Notion?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. Notion AI is built into the Notion product and only works on content that lives inside your Notion workspace. It cannot access external documents, run standalone workflows, or operate outside of Notion. Claude, by contrast, works across any context and can integrate with external tools via its API and MCP connections."}}]}</script>
